dct_title_s: Tourist map of Bhubaneshwar / produced for the Department of Tourism, Govt. of Orissa, by South Eastern Circle, Survey of India. (Recto)
dct_description_sm: Selected buildings shown pictorially. Panel title: Bhubaneshwar tourist map. Includes inset showing tourist centres around Bhubaneshwar, distance list, and location map. Color illustration with description and maps of Bhubaneshwar and vicinity and Nandankanan with index on verso.
dct_creator_sm: Survey of India. South Eastern Circle
